subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Armed with a big serve and a sizzling forehand, Golubev, the 98th-ranked player in the world, gave Nadal all the topspin he could handle before falling, 6-3, 7-6 (1), 7-5.
